Waterproof, Completely Ecological Footwear

1k+

Ordered per year

6

Months warranty

Our shoes do not require special care, waterproof, comfortable and safe for the environment.

Nature has given us everything to create a great product

Hemp shoes are environmentally friendly, breathable, durable and softer when worn, so they are good for shoes.

  • Environmentally friendly and growing fast.
  • Hemp is hypoallergenic and non-irritating to the skin.
  • Extremely strong fibers for use in footwear.
  • Leaves a very small carbon footprint on dehydrogenation.

We select the best fabrics and materials

Hemp thread

Hemp fabric

Recycled rubber

    We have used an eco-friendly insole and outsole made out of recycled rubber. Think of these shoes as your favorite companion to make you physically fit.
